How to change your Google profile picture. (The image that appears as a letter in google docs)

 1. Go to google Drive
 2. Next to your CCPS email, click the 9 dots(In a 3x3 square)
 3. Click more
 4. Click "Classroom"
 5. Scroll down and click the "Student" button
 6. In the top left corner, beside the "Home" text, click the 3 bars
 7. At the bottom of the pop up menu, Click "Settings"
 8. Look around and click the "Change your profile picture" (It looks like a link)
 9. Change your photo and enjoy! This works for all google related things.

Tutorial Made By: Michael Smith
